          "trigger": "Single-account adjustment request exceeding $500 on a consumer account or $5,000 on an enterprise account",
          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "billing_operations_supervisor",
          "rationale": "Adjustments above delegation limits require second-person approval; large unreviewed credits are the classic internal-fraud and write-off leakage vector."
        },
        {
          "trigger": "Usage records sitting in suspense/unguided status for more than 48 hours, or a mediation batch that failed to close",
          "action": "request_more_info",
          "handoffTarget": "mediation_operations",
          "rationale": "Suspense aging past 48 hours risks events falling outside the billable window entirely — permanent leakage — so the guiding failure cause (bad rating group, missing subscriber reference) must be identified before bulk reprocessing."
        }
      ],
